Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two months passed since we started\Nour second year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we had become
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,accustomed to our new classes \Nand to having juniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the biggest event of the year was upon us...\NNo, one of the biggest events in high school:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to me, that day is slightly\Nmore significant than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SCHOOL FIELD TRIP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, are you packed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ssh, they'll hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the dark followers\Nhave not spotted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any loud noises will annoy the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with these on, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have just returned from my mission\Nto summon the Dark Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing these fortifies \Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are equipped with\Nthe power to see isolated worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they look cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get packed and take your bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Travelling to the Island of\N Tsukushi... of Hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you are fully prepared\Nfor a journey to the dark world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is actually less \Nthan before. At first...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's why this little bag smells so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's "carrion" luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather round, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, while you set out \Nfor the battleground...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I, Dekomori, will keep watch over\Nour society like a deity of protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dressed sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am. This is \Nthe school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny could be waiting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now announce the recreation\Nprograms for each group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are prohibited from \Ngoing to the other cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are also prohibited\Nfrom using your cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The speed of sound is impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going quite that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Wicked Lord Shingan sees all.\NThis is not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not the girl who went\Nto her family home last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure do get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take our photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You're going out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go showing it to the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll print it out for you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I am giving you one hour of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet back here at 2 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palace where the imprisoned\Ndragon's soul sleeps...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,banished by the patron saint of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Known as the Dark Dragonius Saint Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now infiltrate under\Nthe dark followers' noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must always anticipate the\Ndark followers' attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought that all this way just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full preparation at all times is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm blinded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combat equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take a commemorative photo\Nof you and Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. This is a school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move closer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to make some\Nmemories with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a copy\Nof the group schedule, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must do something before\NI lose mental capacity and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can that be a messenger sent by my master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here! Dekomori is over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mr. Mushroom is such a fungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem especially enthused about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,napping ever since the \Nnapping club competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up. Wake up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have returned from the dream world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This region is stagnant territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to escape and \Nadvance to another area!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance to where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yayoi Settlement\NMuseum
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TODAY'S ACTIVITIES\NMagatama making\NClay flute making
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Historic ruins containing \Nthe powers of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People lived in this area\Nfrom the Jomon period onward,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there used to be a sea nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversing with the souls\Nwho once lived here so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing. Nibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the whispers of the Light Beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi is here with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on over, don't be \Nshy. Sorry about before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pester you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This seems tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are going out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no need\Nto be so embarrassed, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am bound to Yuta by a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a Lover's Contract, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Eye Dark Curve!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misbehave in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each room's group must bathe\Naccording to the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you don't want her to get\Nworked up about romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:39.69,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the kimonos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.85,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wear my sweats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.47,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my shampoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever she starts to think hard\Nabout it, she gets confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.83,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.98,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of romance doesn't\Nfit into her chunibyo delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take care of her for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Don't you want to be with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, but so many people are watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka can't handle that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually kind of nice, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! What in the world\Ndo those two want from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay 'cause I just put these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,All-Porpoise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My "all-porpoise" socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to discuss the Dark \NFlame Master and my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a bad mood, Deko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am! I have \Nalways showed restraint
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhether they want to be together or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they want to be together or don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean. \NThey're like that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always so secretive.\NIt makes me feel like the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little sister to Dark Flame Master\Nand Ghelzonianses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Kuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love your big brother, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they're all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:26.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,All\NPorpoise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you really going in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. You should call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opinion doesn't count\Nbecause you have Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Isshiki! Isshiki's been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WOMEN'S\NBATH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly mixed up the men's\Nand the women's baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we use Route B?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls in our class\Nwill be done bathing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a crush? \NAll the boys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Aren't you \Ngoing out with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, not anyone in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a boyfriend last year, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the interrogation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been good friends with Togashi\Nsince you started high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We thought maybe\Nyou guys went out at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then maybe you were in\Na love triangle with Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my personal viewpoint\Nas the Love Meister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've never been in a relationship,\Nnever mind a love triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More girls are like that than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like seasoned veterans\Nwhen they're only amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some experience, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes. In a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In middle school, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But when you were in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you go around saying\Nyou were 1,200 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was talking about it.\NThey say you still do it on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani!\NWe're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE WHISPERS OF\NMORI SUMMER\NLOVE - LIFE - FORTUNE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Horoscopes for the\N12 Constellations
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,COMMENTS:\NMori Summer helped me with my love life.\NI am happily dating my crush.\NMori Summer's advice did the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that look. So, it is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-n-no, it isn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I carry on like a Middle Two kid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nnow that I'm in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, we have to be up early. Time to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a will 'o' the wisp\Ncrept up beside the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, forget the ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather hear how far \Nyou've gotten, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far I've gotten with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know. With Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we really need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You started going out during\Nlast year's Culture Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A month later comes the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a few dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you spend Christmas Eve together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, fruitful offline life!\NShatter into a billion pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! Don't reshape my love life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no. Like I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-we haven't yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible. You're a healthy,\Nhot-blooded high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer in writhing agony and vanish,\Nfruitful offline life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta wonder why you feel\Nthe need to lie at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then bring Takanashi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I... do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers are patrolling the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! I just saw a strange \Nlight in the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just heard a woman moaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace, rest in peace, rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? What if someone saw you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. My dark exorcizing\Ndefensive application...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,renders me visually\Nunrecognizable to commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing worth mentioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, why don't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be asleep by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's with Dark Flame Master\Nat this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I doubt they're up to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that a girl's bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still awake in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! It's the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can you please come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I hear strange voices\Nfrom over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better go while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I heard strange voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? There's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they came from further inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your room. You could be\Nsent home early if you're spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a barrier between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was the dark followers' doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier that prevented me\Nfrom approaching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a form of psychological attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't running from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wasn't avoiding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to say you're too shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we have free time tomorrow,\Ndo you wanna look around together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it love, or is it something greater?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it is yet, \Nbut I had the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that slowly but surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that something was gradually\Nbeing set in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka and I greeted the new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll be doing her own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your power. We need to contain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our day alone together begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be\NContinued
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
